-- Fundraiser Nemazee Is Sentenced to 12 Years for $292 Million Bank Fraud
-- David Glovin
-- 2010-07-15T14:53:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-15/fundraiser-nemazee-is-sentenced-to-12-years-for-292-million-bank-fraud.html

          
          
             Hassan Nemazee, a fundraiser for
President Barack Obama and Secretary of State Hillary Clinton,
was sentenced to 12 years in prison for cheating Citigroup Inc.,
HSBC Holdings Plc and Bank of America Corp. of $292 million.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
David Glovin in New York at 
 dglovin@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        